.expo/
node_modules/

# expo prebuild output, regenerated by `expo run:ios` / `expo run:android`.
# Leaving it visible lets a `git commit -a` sweep the whole native project in,
# and ignoring it is what makes @expo/fingerprint treat this app as CNG and skip
# hashing it. Anchored so it cannot also swallow modules/*/ios, which is source.
/ios
/android
